Package akka.routing

Class RoutedActorCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.ActorCell
      • akka.routing.RoutedActorCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractActor.ActorContext, ActorContext, ActorRefFactory, Cell, ClassicActorContextProvider, Children, DeathWatch, Dispatch, FaultHandling, ReceiveTimeout
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResizablePoolCell
    public class RoutedActorCell
extends ActorCell
    Add routees to the Router. Messages in flight may still be routed to the old Router instance containing the old routees.
